67
00:04:32,905 --> 00:04:34,986
I am new to Medford.

68
00:04:35,006 --> 00:04:36,087
I've been here for about a year and a half.

69
00:04:37,167 --> 00:04:41,149
But I feel like this, it is a community that could take this on.

70
00:04:42,249 --> 00:04:42,630
So that's.

71
00:04:43,810 --> 00:04:44,831
Thank you very much, Emily.

