01:21:35,451 --> 01:21:37,252
Last Friday, October 17th,

1166
01:21:38,832 --> 01:21:48,679
members of the South Method residents together, better known as SMARTO, organized a public safety walk within their neighborhood.

1167
01:21:49,880 --> 01:21:57,005
I just would like to thank Jim Silva, who is the organizer slash founder of SMARTO.

1168
01:21:57,165 --> 01:22:07,853
And as we all know, behind this rail and many residents of South Method, that particular group has been instrumental in getting many initiatives from public safety,

1169
01:22:08,361 --> 01:22:16,686
to streets and sidewalks and a host of issues accomplished through togetherness and through unity.

1170
01:22:17,347 --> 01:22:24,311
And on last Friday, Mr. President, there was roughly 30 residents that showed up for the walk.

1171
01:22:24,892 --> 01:22:35,859
The walk was roughly a mile and a half through many streets in South Method, starting from the Yield Street parking lot and ending up at the Columbus School.

1172
01:22:36,910 --> 01:22:40,694
and back to the South Meffitt Business District.

1173
01:22:41,714 --> 01:22:54,205
