1175
01:23:04,940 --> 01:23:11,203
who's actually patrolling the streets, meet them and say hi to them and see a familiar face, which was nice.

1176
01:23:12,183 --> 01:23:17,746
I attended the walk along with Councilors Caviello and Councilor De La Russo.

1177
01:23:19,346 --> 01:23:25,469
