1178
01:23:26,189 --> 01:23:29,090
There were issues of concern with speeding on our streets.

1179
01:23:29,511 --> 01:23:31,071
There was issues of break-ins.

1180
01:23:31,492 --> 01:23:34,753
There were issues of different activity

1181
01:23:35,186 --> 01:23:39,988
drug activity, criminal activity taking place on our streets, Mr. President.

1182
01:23:40,888 --> 01:24:00,655
The talk also went not only to public safety, but there was issues regarding DPW, the streetlights, many streetlights that were either dim or out altogether, which was brought up before this council several weeks back to improve lighting in that particular area.

1183
01:24:01,336 --> 01:24:04,697
We witnessed a number of double poles up and down the streets.

1184
01:24:05,260 --> 01:24:09,022
that we took and wrote notes on.

1185
01:24:09,462 --> 01:24:17,566
There were also many, many tree stumps that still strewn throughout the sidewalks in South Method.

1186
01:24:18,246 --> 01:24:28,190
And again, we witnessed firsthand traversing the sidewalks with curbs that are raised higher than the sidewalk or a little lower than the sidewalk, which is a trip and hazard.

1187
01:24:28,571 --> 01:24:33,933
We witnessed streets that were in awful deplorable condition.

1188
01:24:34,711 --> 01:24:37,732
to walk on and to drive on, Mr. President.

1189
01:24:38,633 --> 01:24:48,737
