1207
01:27:06,422 --> 01:27:11,724
I think it's probably the most effective way of reaching everyone in the community that would have an interest.

1208
01:27:12,404 --> 01:27:15,505
And I would ask, Mr. President, that we establish

1209
01:27:16,005 --> 01:27:26,292
neighborhood safety walks in every segment and every section of this community with the heads of the different departments.

1210
01:27:26,912 --> 01:27:29,574
